Bundled third-party content
---------------------------

vanilla/   The 29 stock Mann vs. Machine mission scripts that ship with
           Team Fortress 2. Copyright Valve Corporation. Included so the
           app has a reference corpus to open and to test the parser
           against; they are plain-text game scripts present in every
           TF2 installation.

base/      robot_standard.pop, robot_giant.pop and robot_gatebot.pop, the
           stock #base bot template files. Copyright Valve Corporation.
           Required to resolve template inheritance in any mission.

samples_sigdemo.pop
           Sample popfile demonstrating sigsegv-mvm (rafmod) extensions,
           used as a parser test fixture.

Robot class icons are NOT bundled. They are read at runtime from your own
Team Fortress 2 installation (loose files, tf/custom, or tf2_textures_dir.vpk).
Missions that reference custom icons resolve them from the mission folder.

Bot movement behaviour in the map simulation is modelled on the publicly
released Source SDK 2013 (ValveSoftware/source-sdk-2013), used as reference
only; no Valve code is included in this repository.

If you are Valve and want any of the above removed, open an issue.
